        "# Movie Recommendation System Using Collaborative Filtering Techniques\n",
        "### MSc Data Science — 7PAM2002 | University of Hertfordshire\n",
        "**Student:** Charan Ravindran (SRN: 24073840)  \n",
        "**Supervisor:** Ashley Spindler  \n",
        "**Dataset:** MovieLens 100K (GroupLens Research, University of Minnesota)\n",
        "\n",
        "---\n",
        "This notebook implements and evaluates a movie recommendation system on the MovieLens 100K\n",
        "dataset. A popularity-based baseline is compared against an item-based collaborative filtering\n",
        "model using cosine similarity. Evaluation uses Precision@K, Recall@K, and NDCG@K at\n",
        "K ∈ {5, 10, 20} via a leave-one-out temporal protocol.\n",
        "\n",
        "**How to run:** Upload `ml-latest-small.zip` to the Colab session, then click\n",
        "*Runtime → Run All*.\n"
