      "source": [
        "## 6. Recommendation Models\n",
        "\n",
        "Two models are implemented and compared:\n",
        "\n",
        "1. **Popularity-Based Baseline** — ranks all movies by total number of training-set ratings\n",
        "   and returns the top-K to every user identically, regardless of individual history.\n",
        "\n",
        "2. **Item-Based Collaborative Filtering** — for a given user, aggregates cosine similarity\n",
        "   scores between each unrated candidate and all movies in the user's training history,\n",
        "   weighting each similarity by the user's own rating. Returns the top-K candidates by\n",
        "   composite relevance score.\n"
      ],
      "id": "ZhLGn8LrTjjK"
    },
